    <ImplicitInverseRef name="sourceLocation" id="82707bf9-d416-472e-a27f-5972d07a0aa7">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="CM_LocationsController"/>
        <text>This reference is ONLY set if this is a YARD Internal job
(ie, been created because of a SWAP).

OR
The job is a REQUEST Type, and we are creating Director tasks
(No TI in that case)

The TI is NOT queued to the swap locations at htis point
so we use the arbiter to store these references when we create
the entries and tasks etc</text>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
